ike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T19:11:53.000Z","msg":"同電視嗰啲好大出入 好悶 唔好咁大期望<br />\n利申local law firm師爺"},{"pid":"dea33bce877c51818234d8b0fc20c887c8b32066","tid":567340,"uid":122285,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T19:57:29.000Z","msg":"係終審法院聽過一次，都係咁岩經過又無野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無衣著要求，但係要尊重場合，好似早走既都要記得鞠躬先<br />\n第一次去聽，好多英文專有名詞，要拎翻譯機"},{"pid":"0bd3a29b9df8d8358cdb2fa55e89d2bb350030c1","tid":567340,"uid":144193,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"0fe9452dff2112125e1a8dd505bc75326462b414","tid":567340,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"756adb8d9e0b10376e3d45ca0f3c1693df77ba17","tid":567340,"uid":144193,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T18:54:13.000Z","msg":"除左部分為保障身分既案件<br />\n一般都開放公眾入場旁 以體現施法透明<br />\n好似係<br />\n<br />\n利申：跟過學校去旁聽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T19:11:44.000Z","msg":"旁聽咩案? 衣著有冇要求, 要西裝恤衫?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:39:27.000Z","msg":"普普通通就可以<br />\n當然晤好背心踢拖la<br />\n<br />\n不過建議你唔好太大期望<br />\n好似樓上巴打講 其實好悶<br />\n好多都只係程序野<br />\n冇電視劇果d唇槍舌戰"},{"pid":"9f5a483458ea6fbe36e7bac938594976f8ca0001","tid":567340,"uid":29914,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:40:38.000Z","msg":"open to public 就得，如果寫住in chamber就唔得"},{"pid":"b5ef3f44bb11f861213c2ba3f22f248bdf844e9d","tid":567340,"uid":106326,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:42:37.000Z","msg":"好多義士上庭個排成日去<br />\n個官同啲律師講野細聲到乜都聽唔到<br />\n之後成日都係見到啲南亞種上庭，唔係傷人偷野就犯毒"},{"pid":"eed9c02addf0c7cf9de06914c1ffef5599d8cae7","tid":567340,"uid":59541,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b5ef3f44bb11f861213c2ba3f22f248bdf844e9d","tid":567340,"uid":106326,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:42:37.000Z","msg":"好多義士上庭個排成日去<br />\n個官同啲律師講野細聲到乜都聽唔到<br />\n之後成日都係見到啲南亞種上庭，唔係傷人偷野就犯毒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T06:01:11.000Z","msg":"南亞仔10個衰9個係dd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999a35b399de6d8443058df25991b080c089864a","tid":567340,"uid":26071,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T02:42:40.000Z","msg":"裁判同地區法院就容易入手d<br />\n大部份都係中文聆訊 fact finding為主 間中有d 九唔搭八嘅證人都幾好笑 有時覺得裁判官忍到笑好勁<br />\n<br />\n高院就比較technical 同埋審好耐 主要係圍繞唔同legal principles既爭議"},{"pid":"c843a1fe5779f4203aea059c624cbd1e032ded54","tid":567340,"uid":158145,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T02:47:59.000Z","msg":"一陣搵你做陪審團你就喊都冇謂"},{"pid":"4fe7bfde55b003e8fd1b2378836f0d47b7e61380","tid":567340,"uid":24668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f5a483458ea6fbe36e7bac938594976f8ca0001","tid":567340,"uid":29914,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:40:38.000Z","msg":"open to public 就得，如果寫住in chamber就唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T02:51:37.000Z","msg":"in chamber都可以 (但唔一定) open to public"},{"pid":"759b7d51ad3dc8955327b0bbd01879277f304d32","tid":567340,"uid":33235,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T03:45:56.000Z","msg":"去過區域法院<br />\n<br />\n聽過兩個庭<br />\n<br />\n1.）一個係女人呃老綜，之前判左佢社會服務令同嘔返D錢，但佢又無做到，仲籍口多多，比個官即場鬧到反艇。<br />\n<br />\n2.）一單普通襲擊，個醉酒佬推個男人，我入去聽果陣已經係宣判，個判詞都幾悶下，反而最精采係個控方律師定辯方律師漏左唔知乜野報告比個官，比個官又係鬧到反艇，個律師企係到成個小學生咁真陰公<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論係法官鬧人係勁到你想搵個位反駁都無，零死角。"},{"pid":"4a64e13c084425665ef52f3d49a0f131cf6405b2","tid":567340,"uid":29914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fe7bfde55b003e8fd1b2378836f0d47b7e61380","tid":567340,"uid":24668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f5a483458ea6fbe36e7bac938594976f8ca0001","tid":567340,"uid":29914,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T03:40:38.000Z","msg":"open to public 就得，如果寫住in chamber就唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T02:51:37.000Z","msg":"in chamber都可以 (但唔一定) open to public"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T03:54:29.000Z","msg":